Google is sending emails to certain customers offering them a 20% discount on the Pixel 2 or Pixel 2 XL, 9to5Google reported. Qualifying customers can apply the discount to any Pixel 2, regardless of colour or storage capacity. The reduced pricing is as follows: Google’s email thanks the recipient for being a loyal Nexus owner, but according to reports, there are people who have only owned two Nexus devices that received the offer – while others who have owned more did not receive it.